{"type":"message","id":"85f6b699","parentId":"847c072f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T21:24:31.493Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 05:24 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态（2025-2026年）：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型：政策补贴、AI应用、信创要求等\n2. 智能安防：市场数据、技术趋势、国产替代进展\n3. 网络系统集成：SD-WAN、云网融合等\n4. IT运维服务：AIOps、智能运维等\n\n请整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1773955471488}}
